\id GAL – Uare 
\h Galatia 
\toc3 Gal 
\toc2 Galatia 
\toc1 Galatia Ekalesia veize Pauloꞌa Mirihiroteꞌe Soꞌaḡa 
\mt1 Galatia  
\mt2 Galatia Ekalesia veize Pauloꞌa Mirihiroteꞌe Soꞌaḡa  
\imt1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa  
\ip Soꞌa ꞌahiꞌe Pauloꞌa Galatia habaꞌano ekalesia veize mirihiro. Pauloꞌe ibite zeḡe habao mada nu radiunu. Iuda ekalesia azaḡa nuꞌa Iesu mazao fieꞌenaꞌa, Mose goro ḡoeꞌa zuni hegotiro. Ze ꞌouge haḡadu Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa reꞌuma rae ziro. Zeꞌa Iuda mene azaḡa zuni Iesu mazao fieꞌenaꞌa, Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegotine Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa reꞌuma rae ihoziro. Pauloꞌa soꞌa ꞌahi zamaḡano zeḡe ḡoereꞌe veꞌoḡa rae fureniro. Mene Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, rehano Iesu mazao fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano daꞌo Badiꞌa ubumao emeꞌe duduḡa reꞌuma rae ihoziro.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Eḡe, Pauloꞌe vazeꞌa teꞌoteꞌohadu apostolo vazeḡano mene reiro, zu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ohohadu apostolo vazeḡano mene reiro. Rehano Iesu Keriso ebu rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano ani bare ḡaboniroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa, emeḡe Mamaꞌa ohohadu apostolo vazeḡano reiro.  
\v 2 Eḡeꞌa eḡe teite radiuꞌeteꞌe ekalesiaḡa nego nabudi niduꞌa teite Galatia habaꞌano ekalesia ꞌahogaꞌahoga veize soꞌa ꞌadi miriheꞌohe.   
\p
\v 3 Badiꞌa emeḡe Mama zu Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Kerisoꞌa zae mazao manoḡa zu zama roḡeḡa ziniꞌenoꞌi.  
\v 4 Izidi madaḡa sauꞌanonoꞌo eme bohafe bufoga veize, Iesu Kerisoꞌa Badiꞌa emeḡe Mama ura idunaḡano emeḡe haḡai sauꞌa rae modifine ane bare dibuꞌiro.   
\p
\v 5 Badiꞌa ni mae ḡihinihi, onamo radiu tuḡutuḡu. Amen.   
\s1 Keriso Hari Manoḡaꞌe Tiba Daꞌo  
\p
\v 6 Kerisoꞌa fureniroteꞌe manoḡaḡa zamaḡano zaeꞌa radoga veize Badiꞌaꞌa zae huziro. Rehano za Badiꞌa ḡarihe fase modadu hari manoḡa ꞌahoga mae ḡihineꞌe ꞌahine, e zaguzagauꞌohe.  
\v 7 Hube hune hari manoḡa ꞌahogaꞌe oꞌoꞌa, rehano vaze nuꞌa za mae ꞌadaꞌadazeꞌohe zu Keriso hari manoḡa ḡihunihi raꞌohe.  
\v 8 Rehano emeḡe ga adureonoꞌo tuḡure viganiꞌa zuni ibite emeꞌa zae mazao haramiroteꞌe hariḡa manoḡa mene haramadu hari manoḡa ꞌahoga zae mazao haramine, Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo radiu tuḡutuḡu adugaḡa hidiꞌuma!  
\v 9 Emeꞌa ibite ziroteꞌe teige, e izidi bare ziꞌohe. Iniuꞌa eḡe mazaonoꞌo igiroteꞌe hariḡa manoḡa zae mazao mene haramadu hari manoḡa nunu zae mazao haramine, aniꞌe radiu tuḡutuḡu adugaḡa hidiꞌuma!   
\p
\v 10 E vazeꞌa eḡe ḡoereꞌe duduḡa rae mae ḡihinifine izidi inareꞌehe? Ga Badiꞌaꞌa eḡe ḡoereꞌe duduḡa rae mae ḡihinifine inareꞌehe? Eḡeꞌa vaze matuꞌozoga veize inareꞌehe? Eꞌa izidi zuni vaze matuꞌozoga veize inarifone, eꞌe Keriso mene tuḡure vazeḡa reifo.   
\s1 Pauloꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa Apostolo Vazeḡano Ohoniro  
\p
\v 11 Nego nabudi, eḡeꞌa haramiroteꞌe hariḡa manoḡaꞌe vazeonoꞌo mene arirotaꞌaꞌe zaꞌa ederoga e urateꞌohe.  
\v 12 Hari manoḡa aꞌe vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa mene iniro zu mene ihohiro. Rehano Iesu Kerisoꞌa hari manoḡa eꞌe eḡe mazao rae furenadu eḡeꞌa meiro.   
\p
\v 13 Zaꞌe ibite eḡeꞌa Iuda azaḡa kuru ibiḡa hegotiroteꞌe madaḡano haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa igiro. Eḡeꞌa Badiꞌa mone ekalesia azaḡa aduga boro ziniro zu ruizihi reiro.  
\v 14 Eꞌa Iuda azaḡa kuru ibiḡano eꞌe goroḡa ḡoeꞌa inare hegotiro. Eꞌe moneo e Iuda azaḡa boꞌaḡano eḡe teite muri tiba azaḡa ḡehaḡa ufeta vitiziro. Ebu eḡe vouḡa haḡai hegote hunihi rae ufeta inariro.  
\v 15 Rehano e ꞌizema fureranogano, Badiꞌaꞌa e avo ohohiro zu aniꞌa eḡe mazao manoḡa furenadu eḡe huhiro.  
\v 16 Eḡeꞌa Iuda mene azaḡa mazao Ubuga hari manoḡa haramifine, aniꞌa matuꞌeꞌenaꞌa, eḡe mazao Ubuga mae fureniro. Eꞌe madaḡano e vaze vaḡe mene onamadu zeḡe teite mene ḡoꞌaniro.  
\v 17 Ebu eḡe ibite vitihe apostolo azaḡano reiroteꞌe azaḡa teite ḡoerihi radu Ierusalema mene itiro. Rehano Arabia habaꞌa onamadu eꞌea radiunu, ebu vesuꞌu Damaseko bariro.   
\p
\v 18 Ebu Iesuꞌa eḡe mazao fureraroteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo muri uḡidu enogano, e Petero\f + \fr 1:18 \fqa Kefa \f* ḡianoga rae Ierusalema itiro ebu ane teite mada 15 radiro.  
\v 19 Eꞌe madaḡano apostolo vazeḡa ꞌahoga mene horoniro, rehano Zuhiꞌa Boro negoḡa Iakobo daꞌo horoniro.  
\v 20 Eḡeꞌa zae veize ꞌadi miriheꞌetaꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa ubumao hube hune mene ḡuriro ḡoeꞌa.   
\p
\v 21 Ebu e Ierusalema mode iḡunadu Siria zu Kilikia habaꞌa onamiro.  
\v 22 Eꞌanoꞌo Iudea habaꞌano Keriso mone ekalesia azaḡaꞌe e mene ederiro.  
\v 23 Zeꞌe harihe daꞌo ꞌahige iginu, “Ibite aduga rifidoteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa emeꞌa fieꞌeteꞌe mae vaḡinihi rae inariro. Rehano izidiꞌe ani Keriso mazao fieꞌeteꞌe moneo harameꞌohe.”  
\v 24 Ze naginiꞌa eḡe mazao fureraroteꞌe egadu Badiꞌa niguniro.   
\c 2  
\s1 Apostolo Azaḡaniꞌa Paulo mae Ḡihiniro  
\p
\v 1 Muri 14 enogano e Banabasi teite Tito zamahanadu Ierusalema bare itiro.  
\v 2 Badiꞌaꞌa, “Itoꞌi,” rae ehadu eꞌa itiro. Itadu e Iuda mene azaḡa mazao hari manoḡa harameꞌeteꞌe moneo ekalesia azaḡa meꞌodoziniro. Ekalesia azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa teiteꞌe avo nuꞌoranadu meꞌodoziniro. Mazaḡa ibite eḡeꞌa gaue arirotaꞌaꞌe zu izidi gaueꞌetaꞌaꞌe huga oꞌoꞌano rouga e mene uratiro.  
\v 3 Tito zuni eḡe teite eꞌea radiro. Aniꞌe Giriki vazeḡa rehano, ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ani ahiꞌa rana iḡuri haḡaoga mene teꞌoteꞌoniro.  
\v 4 Mazaḡa ḡuriro ekalesia azaḡa nuꞌa emeḡe ekalesia zamaḡano sifu diuḡi ariro. Ebu ze emeḡeꞌa Keriso Iesu teite tiburanadu Mose goro ḡoeꞌanonoꞌo bohafe bufiroteꞌe rihinoga uratiro, ebu emeḡe tutufadu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌeteꞌe tuḡure azaḡano rouga uratiro.  
\v 5 Rehano zaeꞌa hari manoḡa moneo ḡoere huga iḡaiḡa obone giganoga veize, eme zeḡe ḡoere tahiḡa zu mene mae ḡihiniro.   
\p
\v 6 Ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe nize boro rehano, e ze mene zamareꞌohe, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa vaze enone daꞌo ḡianadu zeꞌe manoḡa ga sauꞌa rae mene raꞌohe. Zeꞌa e Iuda mene azaḡa mazao harameꞌeteꞌe hariḡa manoḡa moneo ḡoereni ꞌahoga mene ihiro.  
\v 7 U zeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa Iuda azaḡa\f + \fr 2:7 \fqa ahiri rana iḡuri haḡairoteꞌe azaḡa \f* mazao hari manoḡa harameꞌeteꞌe gauḡa Petero haroteꞌe teige, Iuda mene azaḡa\f + \fr 2:7 \fqa ahiri rana iḡuri mene haḡairoteꞌe azaḡa \f* mazao harameꞌeteꞌe gauḡa eḡe inirotaꞌaꞌe ederiro.  
\v 8 Badiꞌaꞌa ane inaraḡa Petero hanadu Iuda azaḡa veize apostolo gauḡa haroteꞌe teige, Badiꞌaꞌa inaraḡa eḡe enadu Iuda mene azaḡa veize apostolo gauḡa iniro.  
\v 9 Iakobo, Petero zu Ioaneꞌe ekalesia boꞌaḡano ne gadoḡa heuḡa. Ze Badiꞌaꞌa eḡe mazao manoḡa fureniroteꞌe ederirotene, eḡe zu Banabasi teite unihifine obotitiro. Ebu emeꞌe Iuda mene azaḡa vaḡe onamiꞌuma, u zeꞌe Iuda azaḡa vaḡe onamiꞌuma rae ḡoere idaniro.  
\v 10 Ze emeꞌa zahara azaḡa zamaradu danazoga veize daꞌo umifiro. Aꞌe eḡeꞌa zuni hube hune haḡae inare ariroteꞌe gauḡa.   
\s1 Pauloꞌa Petero Roniro  
\p
\v 11 Rehano Peteroꞌa Antioka arirotene, aniꞌa veꞌoḡa haḡadu eḡeꞌa ani ubuma ꞌue roniro.  
\v 12 Aniꞌe Iakobo mazaonoꞌo Iuda azaḡa nuꞌa ꞌizema arogano Iuda mene azaḡa ekalesiaḡa teite tiburu ogaudo. Rehano zeꞌa feurirotene, aniꞌe Iuda mene azaḡa mazaonoꞌo ꞌie baradu zeḡe teite mene ogau tiburaro, mazaḡa aniꞌe Iuda azaḡa\f + \fr 2:12 \fqa ahiri rana iḡuri haḡairoteꞌe azaḡa \f* rihoziro.  
\v 13 Aniꞌa ꞌougirotene, eꞌea radiunuteꞌe Iuda azaḡa zuni ani hegotadu zama guhi azaḡa teige veꞌoriro. Ebu Banabasi zuni zeḡe teite veꞌoriro.   
\p
\v 14 E zeḡeꞌa hari manoḡa huga mene ibi duduḡano hegotinuteꞌe horonirotene, zeḡe niduꞌa ubumao Petero niro, “Ḡaꞌe Iuda vazeḡa rehano, Iuda azaḡa goro ḡoeꞌa mene hegoteꞌenaꞌa, Iuda mene azaḡa teige radiuꞌohe. U ḡaꞌe nougadu Iuda mene azaḡaꞌe Iuda azaḡa teige radoꞌi rae raꞌohe?”   
\s1 Fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano Badiꞌa ubumao Duduḡa rae Raꞌohe  
\p
\v 15 Emeꞌe fureraroteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo Iuda azaḡa. Ebu Iuda mene azaḡaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa rae huzeꞌohe, u emeꞌe ze mene heuḡa raꞌohe.  
\v 16 Rehano eme edeḡa, Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegotadu Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae mene raꞌohe, rehano Iesu Keriso mazao fiadu Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae raꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo emeḡe zuni Keriso Iesu mazao firo. Aꞌe, mene emeꞌa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, rehano Keriso mazao fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae reifine reiro. Mazaḡa iniu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa.  
\v 17 Emeꞌa Keriso mazao fiadu Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae rouga veize inareꞌenaꞌa, emeḡe zuni haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa rae raꞌeteꞌe furenine, Kerisoꞌe emeḡeꞌa haḡai sauꞌa haḡaoga veize tutufe veꞌofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa raꞌehe? Mene hune!  
\v 18 E Mose goro ḡoeꞌa modiro. Eḡeꞌa eꞌe bare meine, e eḡeꞌa bare goro ḡoeꞌa varadeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa rae reꞌuma.  
\v 19 E Mose goro ḡoeꞌa uꞌano rudanadu eꞌe veize mene bare radiuꞌohe. Aꞌe Badiꞌa veize radifine raꞌohe.  
\v 20 E Keriso teite satauro rana rudaro. Eꞌanoꞌo e eḡeꞌa bare mene radiuꞌohe, rehano eḡe zamaoꞌe Kerisoꞌa radiuꞌohe. E ahiri hina raha ꞌadao radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe, eḡe zamare borofadu eḡe veize ḡaboneḡa ahetiroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa Ubuga mazao fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, radiuꞌohe.  
\v 21 Eꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa eḡe mazao fureniroteꞌe manoḡaḡa mene hezahohauꞌohe, mazaḡa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegotadu Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae reifone, Kerisoꞌe foure rudaro rae reifo.   
\c 3  
\s1 Iesu mazao Fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano Duduḡa rae Raꞌohe  
\p
\v 1 Galatia ekalesia azaḡa, zaꞌe kauriḡa! Iesu Kerisoꞌa zae veize satauro rana rudaroteꞌe eḡeꞌa doḡoꞌani ihozadu zaeꞌa ubumazeo horoniroteꞌe heuḡa rehano, zamazeꞌe iniuꞌa aro?  
\v 2 E ḡau tiba daꞌo zae mazaonoꞌo ederihi raꞌohe. Zaeꞌa Vine Zaḡoḡa meirotaꞌaꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegotiroteꞌe uꞌano ga emeḡeꞌa haramiroteꞌe hariḡa manoḡa egadu eꞌe mae ḡihiniroteꞌe uꞌano?  
\v 3 Za ufeta kauriḡahe? Zaꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ibitozeadu Iesu mazao fieꞌeteꞌe ḡadaheniro, rehano izidi zaꞌe vaze inaraḡa hina hauḡihi raꞌehe?  
\v 4 Ibite zaeꞌa aduga ḡehaḡa hidirotaꞌaꞌe huga oꞌoꞌahe? Aꞌe hube hune huḡeta!  
\v 5 Nagini uꞌano Badiꞌaꞌa za Vine Zaḡoḡa ziniꞌohe zu zae boꞌaḡano haḡai gigiꞌaḡa haḡaeꞌohe? Zaeꞌa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌeteꞌe uꞌano ga zaeꞌa hari manoḡa egadu eꞌe mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe uꞌano?   
\p
\v 6 Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, “Aberahamoꞌa Badiꞌa mazao fiadu Badiꞌaꞌa aniꞌe duduḡa rae mae ḡihiniro.”\x + \xo 3:6 \xt Ḡadaheḡa 15:6 \x*  
\v 7 Eꞌanoꞌo fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Aberahamo mariga rae ederoꞌi.  
\v 8 Iuda mene azaḡaꞌe fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa reꞌuma rae raꞌeteꞌe Buka Zaḡoḡano irina ihoziro. Ebu Buka Zaḡoḡanonoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa eꞌe hariḡa manoḡa irina Aberahamo niro, “Haba niduꞌa zamaḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe ḡae mazaonoꞌo manohuga hidiꞌuma.”\x + \xo 3:8 \xt Ḡadaheḡa 12:3, 18:18, 22:18\x*  
\v 9 Aberahamoꞌe firoteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahine, ani teite fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zuni manohuga hideꞌohe.   
\p
\v 10 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegotadu Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa reꞌuma rae raꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa aduga tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma. Mazaḡa Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, “Iniu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa bukaḡa zamaḡano mirihiroteꞌe goroḡa niduꞌa iḡaiḡa mene hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa radiu tuḡutuḡu adugaḡa hidiꞌuma.”\x + \xo 3:10 \xt Goro 27:26 \x*  
\v 11 Hube hune iniuꞌa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegotadu Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa. Mazaḡa Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, “Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa azaḡaꞌe zeꞌa fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, radiꞌuma.”\x + \xo 3:11 \xt Habaku 2:4 \x*  
\v 12 Mose goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe fieꞌeteꞌeanoꞌo mene fureraro. Buka Zaḡoḡanoꞌe ꞌahige rae mirihiro, “Mose goro ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa hegoteꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa ꞌouge haḡadu ḡabode radiꞌuma.”\x + \xo 3:12 \xt Dibuꞌo 18:5\x*   
\p
\v 13 Mose goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe emeḡe rana radiu tuḡutuḡu adugaḡa tiꞌohe. Rehano emeḡe rana tiroteꞌe radiu tuḡutuḡu adugaḡa aꞌe Kerisoꞌa ane rana teadu radiu tuḡutuḡu adugaḡanonoꞌo eme bohafe bufiro. Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, “Ire rana midau tiroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe radiu tuḡutuḡu adugaḡa hidiroteꞌe azaḡa.”\x + \xo 3:13 \xt Goro 21:23\x*  
\v 14 Kerisoꞌa ꞌouge haḡairotaꞌaꞌe, Badiꞌaꞌa Aberahamo haroteꞌe manohugaḡa Keriso Iesu uꞌano Iuda mene azaḡa zuni zinifine, ebu emeꞌa fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, Badiꞌaꞌa rifiꞌuma rae ḡoitoriroteꞌe Vineḡa Zaḡoḡa emeḡeꞌa meifine raꞌohe.   
\s1 Mose Goro Ḡoeꞌa zu Ḡoitore Ḡoeꞌa  
\p
\v 15 Nego nabudi, emeḡe radone zamaḡano hari idaidaḡa ꞌahoga ziꞌuma. Vaze aheuꞌa ḡoere idanadu ḡoitorine, vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa hena mene fahiꞌuma ga ḡoere ꞌahoga mene bare ragate tiꞌuma.  
\v 16 Badiꞌaꞌa Aberahamo zu ane mariga ꞌahoga teite ḡoitoriro. Buka Zaḡoḡano, “Vaze ḡehaḡa,” rae ihozifine, “Marigo duḡuru teite ḡoitoriro,” rae mene reiro, rehano “Vaze tiba daꞌo,” rae ihozifine, “Marigo ꞌahoga teite ḡoitoriro,” rae reiro. Aꞌe Keriso.  
\v 17 Eḡeꞌa reihi raꞌeteꞌe hugaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe: Badiꞌaꞌa ibite Aberahamo teite ḡoitoriro. Ebu muri 430 enogano Moseonoꞌo goro ḡoeꞌa rifiro. Eꞌanoꞌo Mose goro ḡoeꞌaniꞌa Badiꞌa ḡoitore ḡoeꞌa fahadu huga oꞌoꞌa rae rougaꞌe mene idaḡa.  
\v 18 Emeꞌa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, Badiꞌa emeḡe Mamaꞌa rifiꞌeteꞌe toheḡa meine, aꞌe mene Badiꞌaꞌa Aberahamo teite ḡoitoriroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa uꞌano maꞌeteꞌe toheḡa. Badiꞌaꞌa Aberahamo teite ḡoitoriroteꞌe uꞌano, Moga Badiꞌaꞌa hauꞌeteꞌe toheḡa Aberahamo haro.   
\p
\v 19 Tena Mose goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe nagini veize? Aꞌe vazeꞌa haḡai sauꞌa haḡaine, zeꞌe veꞌoḡa haḡaeha rae ihozifine ragate mirihiroteꞌe goroḡa. Mose goro ḡoeꞌaniꞌa ꞌouge gauinu, onamo Aberahamo mariga ꞌahoga, Badiꞌaꞌa ḡoitoriroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa ariro. Mose goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ane tuḡure vigaonoꞌo nema vazeḡa Mose hanadu haḡairo.  
\v 20 Vaze nuꞌa ḡoitoreꞌetene, nema vazeḡa urateꞌohe. U Badiꞌaꞌa Aberahamo teite ḡoitorirotene, Badiꞌa tibuhuga daꞌo haḡairo.   
\s1 Mose Goro Ḡoeꞌaꞌe Nagini Veize?  
\p
\v 21 ꞌOugadu Mose goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ḡoitoriroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa hezaohauꞌehe? Mene hune! Badiꞌaꞌa ḡabone rifiꞌeteꞌe goroḡa ḡoeꞌa rififone, emeꞌe goro ḡoeꞌa eꞌe hegotadu Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae reifo.  
\v 22 Rehano Buka Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ḡau niduꞌaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa inaraḡa hegoteꞌeteꞌe ḡuꞌa azaḡa teige radiuꞌohe rae raꞌohe. Aꞌe, Iesu Keriso mazao fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, Badiꞌaꞌa ḡoitoriroteꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zinifine ꞌouge reiro.   
\p
\v 23 Keriso mazao fieꞌeteꞌe madaḡa ꞌizema arogano, Mose goro ḡoeꞌaniꞌa emeꞌe ane hegoteꞌeteꞌe tuḡure azaḡa teige ani ꞌuꞌuḡano obofe tiro, onao emeꞌa Keriso mazao fiteꞌe madaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa furenofiro.  
\v 24 Eꞌanoꞌo Mose goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe emeḡe ibitofiꞌeteꞌe ihoreḡa vazeḡano reiro, onao Kerisoꞌa ariro. Aꞌe, emeꞌa fiadu Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae rouga veize reiro.  
\v 25 Izidi eme Keriso mazao fieꞌeteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa ariro ꞌahine, Mose goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe mene bare emeḡe ibitofiꞌeteꞌe ihoreḡa vazeḡa raꞌohe.   
\p
\v 26 Zae niduꞌa fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, Keriso Iesu teite tiburanadu Badiꞌa ubugaubuga reiro.  
\v 27 Zae niduꞌaꞌe babatiso madu Keriso teite tiburaro ebu dabua iziga haḡairoteꞌe teige, zaꞌe Keriso heuḡa reiro.  
\v 28 Zaꞌe mene vaze nunu. Iuda vazeḡa ga mene Iuda vazeḡa, tuḡure vazeḡa ga mene tuḡure vazeḡa, ohoze ga roḡaeꞌe oꞌoꞌa. Za Keriso Iesu teite tiburanadu zae niduꞌaꞌe tiba.  
\v 29 Za Keriso mone reine, zaꞌe Aberahamo mariga ebu Badiꞌaꞌa ḡoitoriroteꞌe idunaḡano Moze Badiꞌaꞌa ziniꞌeteꞌe toheḡa hiditeꞌe azaḡa.   
\c 4  
\p
\v 1 E ꞌahi reihi. Moga tohe niduꞌa meiteꞌe ubugaꞌe ḡau niduꞌa meiroteꞌe vazeḡa rehano, komeꞌa madaḡanoꞌe aniꞌe tuḡure vazeḡa heuḡa.  
\v 2 Ani komeꞌa madaḡano, aniꞌe ane taufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu ane ḡau taufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ḡoere egoziniꞌohe, onamo moganiꞌa ohoniroteꞌe madaḡa meꞌuma.  
\v 3 Eꞌe teige, emeꞌe komeꞌa madaḡano raha ꞌadi ibitohauꞌeteꞌe viga\f + \fr 4:3 \ft ihoreḡa \f* nunu hegotadu tuḡure azaḡa teige radiunu.  
\v 4 Rehano Badiꞌaꞌa ohoniroteꞌe madaḡa meirotene, Badiꞌaꞌa Ubuga tuḡunadu aniꞌe roḡae ꞌahoga mazaonoꞌo fureraro ebu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌenaꞌa radiro.  
\v 5 Badiꞌaꞌa Ubuga tuḡunirotaꞌaꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌanonoꞌo vaze bohaze buzoga veize, zu emeꞌe Badiꞌa ubuga rae rouga veize reiro.  
\v 6 Zaꞌe Badiꞌa ubuga uꞌano, aniꞌa Ubuga Viga emeḡe zamao tuḡuniro, eꞌanoꞌo Ubuga Viga uꞌano emeꞌa Badiꞌa mazao, “Mama,\f + \fr 4:6 \fqa Aba \f* eḡe Mama,” rae huneꞌohe.  
\v 7 Eꞌanoꞌo zae tibatibaꞌe tuḡure azaḡano mene bare raꞌohe, rehano Badiꞌa ubuga rae raꞌohe. Zaꞌe Badiꞌa ubugaubuga uꞌano, Badiꞌaꞌa ane ubugaubuga ziniteꞌe toheḡa niduꞌa zae zuni ziniꞌuma.   
\s1 Pauloꞌa Galatia Ekalesia Azaḡa Zamare Borofiro  
\p
\v 8 Ibite zaꞌe Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa madaḡano mene badiꞌa huga rae raꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa hegotadu ane tuḡure azaḡano reiro.  
\v 9 Rehano izidi zaꞌe Badiꞌa edeḡa. Hube hune, e Badiꞌaꞌa za ederiro rae reꞌuma. Rehano za nougadu raha ꞌada ibitohauꞌeteꞌe viga nunu bare vaḡeꞌohe? Aꞌe inaraḡa oꞌoꞌa zu huga oꞌoꞌa. Zaꞌe deꞌeguḡa viga hegoteꞌeteꞌe tuḡure azaḡano bare reihi raꞌehe?  
\v 10 Zaeꞌa Iuda azaḡa haḡai teige, mada boro nunu, bato boro nunu, irugu zu nahune madaḡa nunu ebu muri nunu hegoteꞌohe.  
\v 11 ꞌOugadu, “E zae veize gauinutaꞌaꞌe foure reꞌuma ga?” rae zamaheꞌa aduduꞌohe.   
\p
\v 12 Nego nabudi, e umizeꞌohe. Eꞌe Iuda azaḡa goro ḡoeꞌa modadu zae teigiro, eꞌanoꞌo zae zuni eḡe teige Iuda azaḡa goro ḡoeꞌa ago hegotoꞌi. Zaꞌa eḡe mazao veꞌoḡa mene haḡairo.  
\v 13 Za edeḡa, e ugihadu zae vaḡe amiro ebu hari manoḡa zae mazao ḡadahe haramiro.  
\v 14 Za ugihe horonadu zamazeꞌa adudaro gaogi rehano, e mene ovoe ḡiahiro zu mene hezahohiro. Ebu Badiꞌa tuḡure viga ga Iesu Keriso teige mae ḡihihiro.  
\v 15 Eꞌe madaḡano zaeꞌa ufeta matuꞌe rudanadu zaꞌe idaḡa reifone ubumaze ḡude vaḡinadu eḡe inihi rae reifo.\f + \fr 4:15 \ft Paulo ubuma ugiḡeta radu ze ani vetuḡaniro. \f* Eꞌe moneo eꞌa vaze mazao rae furenoga zuni idaḡa. Rehano izidi zae matuꞌu aꞌe nougeha?  
\v 16 Eḡeꞌa ḡoere huga zeadu eꞌe zae agire vazeḡa reirohe?   
\p
\v 17 Ḡuriro ihore azaḡaꞌe zaeꞌa manoḡa mouga veize za mene zamareꞌohe. Zeꞌe eme mazaonoꞌo zae mae vaḡizadu zaeꞌa ze inare hegotoga daꞌo urateꞌohe.  
\v 18 Iniuꞌa zae danazifine inarine, aꞌe manoḡa. Mene eḡeꞌa zae teite radiuꞌeteꞌe madaḡano daꞌo, rehano mada niduꞌa ꞌougine, manoḡa.  
\v 19 Eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa, roḡaeꞌa ene fureneꞌeteꞌe madaḡano gigiꞌa maꞌeteꞌe teige, e zae uꞌano bare gigiꞌa maꞌohe, onamo zaeꞌa Keriso teigiꞌuma.  
\v 20 E izidi zae teite radadu negane roḡeru ḡorezihi raꞌohe, mazaḡa e zae moneo ꞌadaꞌadaheꞌohe.   
\s1 Hagara zu Sara Hari Idaidaḡa  
\p
\v 21 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegote radihi raꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, ehoꞌi! Za Mose goro ḡoeꞌaniꞌa nagini raꞌetaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌahe?  
\v 22 Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro.\x + \xo 4:22 \xt Ḡadaheḡa 16:15, 21:2 \x* Aberahamoꞌe ubuga aheu. ꞌAhogaꞌe tuḡure roḡaeḡaniꞌa fureniro, u ꞌahogaꞌe mene tuḡure roḡaeḡaniꞌa fureniro.  
\v 23 Tuḡure roḡaeḡa mazaonoꞌo fureraroteꞌe ubugaꞌe vaze ahiri ibiḡano fureraro, u mene tuḡure roḡaeḡa mazaonoꞌo fureraroteꞌe ubugaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ḡoitoriroteꞌe ḡoeꞌanonoꞌo fureraro.  
\v 24 Aꞌe hari idaidaḡa raꞌohe. Roḡae aheu aꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa vaze teite ḡoitoriroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa aheu. Roḡae tibaꞌe Hagara. Hagaraꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa Sinai maḡano ziniroteꞌe goroḡa ḡoeꞌa heuḡa. Eꞌe goro ḡoeꞌaniꞌa vaze tutuzadu Hagara ubugaubuga teige, eꞌe goro ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌeteꞌe tuḡure azaḡano mae tiro.  
\v 25 Hagaraꞌe Arabia habaꞌano Sinai maḡa teite idaniro, ebu izidiꞌe Ierusalema ne boro teite idaniro. Ierusalemaꞌe Ierusalema azaḡa teite goro ḡoeꞌa eꞌe hegoteꞌeteꞌe tuḡure azaḡa teige radiuꞌohe.  
\v 26 Rehano adure Ierusalemaḡaꞌe mene tuḡure roḡaeḡa ebu aꞌe emeḡe nanu.  
\v 27 Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro,  
\q1 “Ene mene fureneꞌeteꞌe gabani roḡaeḡa,  
\q2 matuꞌoꞌi!  
\q1 Ene fureneꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa aḡuꞌa roḡaeḡa,  
\q2 agoḡo boro hina, ḡihau ḡoeroꞌi!  
\q1 Mazaḡa iniu ane daꞌo radiuꞌeteꞌe roḡaeḡa ubugaubugaꞌe ḡeharaꞌuma.  
\q1 Zeꞌe iꞌa teite radiuꞌeteꞌe roḡaeḡa ubugaubuga ufeta vitize ḡeharaꞌuma.”\x + \xo 4:27 \xt Isaia 54:1 \x*   
\p
\v 28 Nego nabudi, zaꞌe Isako teige Badiꞌaꞌa ḡoitoriroteꞌe ubugaubuga.  
\v 29 Rehano Aberahamo madaḡano vaze ahiri ibiḡano fureraroteꞌe ubuganiꞌa Vine Zaḡoḡa gigiꞌaonoꞌo fureraroteꞌe ubuga aduga boro haro. Eꞌe teige, izidi zuni ꞌuguḡaniꞌa fureruꞌohe.  
\v 30 Rehano Buka Zaḡoḡano nouge rae raꞌohe? “Tuḡure roḡaeḡa ubugeta hegozoꞌi, mazaḡa tuḡure roḡaeḡa ubugaꞌe mene tuḡure roḡaeḡa ubuga teite moga tohe mene hune hidiꞌuma.”\x + \xo 4:30 \xt Ḡadaheḡa 21:10\x*  
\v 31 Eꞌanoꞌo, nego nabudi, emeꞌe mene tuḡure roḡaeḡa ubugaubuga, rehano tuḡure mene haḡaeꞌeteꞌe roḡaeḡa ubugaubuga.   
\c 5  
\s1 Kerisoꞌa Emeḡe Bohafe Bufiro  
\p
\v 1 Kerisoꞌa Mose goro ḡoeꞌanonoꞌo emeḡe bohafe bufiroteꞌe uꞌano, emeꞌe bohaꞌa. Eꞌanoꞌo zaꞌe edau gigaruꞌenaꞌa, Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌeteꞌe tuḡure azaḡano aduga ago bare odohoꞌi.   
\p
\v 2 Eḡe, Pauloꞌa ziꞌohe, za faine egoꞌi. Za ahiri rana iḡuri haḡaeꞌeteꞌe mae ḡihinine, Kerisoꞌe zae mazao manoḡa rae mene reꞌuma.  
\v 3 Iniu ahiri rana iḡuri haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa mazao eḡeꞌa bare raꞌohe. Aniꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa zuni hegote huniꞌuma!  
\v 4 Zae boꞌaḡano Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegotadu Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae reihi rae raꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Keriso mazaonoꞌo mae rovoziroteꞌe azaḡa reiro, zu Badiꞌaꞌa zeḡe mazao fureneꞌeteꞌe manoḡaḡanonoꞌo uitadu vaḡiniro.  
\v 5 Emeꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡaonoꞌo fiadu Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae rouga mae ḡihineꞌenaꞌa inare guhineꞌohe.  
\v 6 Mazaḡa Keriso Iesu teite tiburaune, ahiri rana iḡuri haḡaeꞌetaꞌaꞌe ga mene haḡaeꞌetaꞌaꞌe mene ḡau boro. Rehano ḡau boroꞌe vaze zamare borofadu zaeꞌa fieꞌeteꞌe fureneꞌohe.   
\p
\v 7 Zaeꞌa ḡoere huga hegoteꞌenaꞌa faine dure arinu. Rehano iniuꞌa za ḡoere huga hegotoga ꞌuiro?  
\v 8 Zama auꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa ꞌuguḡaꞌe za huziroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa mazaonoꞌo mene ariro.  
\v 9 Vazeꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe, “Isiti tahiḡa faseꞌa usuga niduꞌaꞌe mae borofeꞌohe.”  
\v 10 E zaeꞌa ihore nunu mene mae ḡihiniꞌuma rae zamare huneꞌohe, mazaḡa emeꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro teite tiburaro. Iniuꞌa zae zama mae ꞌadaꞌadaneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe aduga hidiꞌuma.  
\v 11 Nego nabudi, eꞌe ahiri rana iḡuri haḡaoꞌi rae izidi zuni haramifone, nougadu eḡeꞌa ꞌize aduga hideꞌohe? ꞌOuge haramifone, e Keriso satauro moneo harameꞌeteꞌe uꞌano hideꞌeteꞌe adugaḡaniꞌa eḡe mazao mene furerafo.  
\v 12 Zae zama mae ꞌadaꞌadaneꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ze zeḡeꞌa bare ohoze ahiri iꞌaḡa are modoga e urateꞌohe!   
\p
\v 13 Nego nabudi, zaꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌanonoꞌo bohaze buzifine Badiꞌaꞌa huziro. Rehano Mose goro ḡoeꞌanonoꞌo bohaꞌa radu ahiri urao haḡai sauꞌa ago haḡaoꞌi. Rehano nego nabudi zamare borofeꞌenaꞌa, danatitoꞌi.  
\v 14 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa niduꞌaꞌe goro ḡoeꞌa tiba ꞌahi zamaḡano, “Za zaeꞌa bare zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe teige nabudize zamare borofoꞌi.”\x + \xo 5:14 \xt Dibuꞌo 19:18 \x*  
\v 15 Rehano zaeꞌa butu maniḡa teige vihotitine zu mau ꞌaune, za zaeꞌa bare ruititiꞌuma. Eꞌanoꞌo tohutohoꞌi!   
\s1 Vine Zaḡoḡa zu Ahiri Haḡaiḡa  
\p
\v 16 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, zaꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe ibiḡano daꞌo radoꞌi, ꞌougine ahiri ura mene hegote radiꞌuma.  
\v 17 Ahiri uraꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa agirohauꞌohe, u Vine Zaḡoḡa uraꞌe ahiriꞌa agirohauꞌohe. Anianineꞌe agirotitadu za zaeꞌa urateꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa haḡaogaꞌe mene idaḡa.  
\v 18 Rehano Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa zae ibitozine, zaꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌenaꞌa, mene radiuꞌohe.   
\p
\v 19 Ahiriꞌa urateꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡaꞌe zaꞌe deheru edereꞌohe. Aꞌe ubuma ḡezo, zama toraga, daro fuꞌa,  
\v 20 ḡuriro badiꞌaḡa mazao kuranoga, naho zu nabone haḡaiḡa, agirotitoga, taꞌirotitoga, ahiahi, maḡunu fuꞌa, ane bare daꞌo zamare borofoga, rovotitoga, zeḡezeḡe avoavo tiburanoga, zeḡezeḡe urao daꞌo haḡaoga,  
\v 21 vaze ḡau horonadu meihi raꞌeteꞌe zamaroneḡa, gagone fuꞌa, haḡai sauꞌa nunuo daꞌo matuꞌe radiu tauḡoga zu eꞌeguḡa haḡaiḡa nunu rae raꞌohe. Ibite e iradugu ḡoeꞌa riḡa ziro rehano, izidi bare ziꞌohe. Haḡai ꞌuguḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe mene Badiꞌa ubugaubuga radu Badiꞌaꞌa ze zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe manoḡaḡa mene hidiꞌuma.   
\p
\v 22 Rehano Vine Zaḡoḡa mazaonoꞌo ꞌahiguḡaniꞌa hudaꞌuma. Aꞌe, zamarotiteꞌeteꞌe, matuꞌeꞌeteꞌe, unihotiteꞌeteꞌe, zama obone giganeꞌeteꞌe, vaze mazao manoḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe, haḡai manoḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe, zama niduꞌa hina haḡaeꞌeteꞌe,  
\v 23 roḡeru haḡaeꞌeteꞌe zu zeḡeꞌa bare haḡai sauꞌa hezahohauꞌeteꞌe raꞌohe. Haḡai ꞌuguḡa agirohauꞌeteꞌe goroḡa ḡoeꞌaꞌe oꞌoꞌa.  
\v 24 Keriso Iesu mone azaḡaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa haḡaihi rae raꞌeteꞌe zamaroneḡa zu ahiri ura haḡaihi rae raꞌeteꞌe zamaroneḡa madu ahirize teite satauro rana ikokoniro.  
\v 25 Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ḡabone iziga rifiro, eꞌanoꞌo eme Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ibitofiꞌeteꞌe idunaḡano radiꞌuma.  
\v 26 Eme emeḡeꞌa bare nife mene hune mae itiꞌuma, mene hune mae maḡunotitiꞌuma zu mene hune ahiahititiꞌuma.   
\c 6  
\s1 Vaze Aduga Odohe Tiburatihi  
\p
\v 1 Nego nabudi, zaꞌe vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ꞌahine, zae boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe horonoꞌidene, zaeꞌa namineꞌenaꞌa, ane haḡai bare mae dudunoꞌi. Ebu zae zuni haḡai sauꞌa haḡaihi rae raꞌeteꞌe zamaroneḡano mene uitifine zaeꞌa bare tohutohoꞌi.  
\v 2 Zae boꞌaḡano nagi aduga zuni odohe tiburanoꞌi. ꞌOugine, zaꞌe Keriso goro ḡoeꞌa hube hune hegote haḡaiꞌuma.  
\v 3 Vaze ꞌahogaꞌe niḡa ꞌoꞌoꞌa rehano, aneꞌa bare niḡa boro rae zamarine, ani ane bare soꞌoneꞌeteꞌe heuḡa.  
\v 4 Vaze tibatibaꞌe haḡaiḡa ḡianadu haḡai manoḡa ꞌahoga horonine, aneꞌa bare ane nigunogaꞌe idaḡa. Rehano vaze ꞌahoga haḡai teiteꞌe mene idatitiꞌuma,  
\v 5 mazaḡa anianine toheꞌe aneaneꞌa odohiꞌuma.   
\p
\v 6 Badiꞌa ḡoere ihoreḡa igiꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡau manoḡa niduꞌa ane ihore vazeḡa teite dainiꞌuma.   
\p
\v 7 Za zae bare ago soꞌozoꞌi. Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa Badiꞌa ni mae ovorogaꞌe mene idaḡa, mazaḡa vazeꞌa nagi ezoga ḡoraune, eꞌe huga hiriviꞌuma.  
\v 8 Iniuꞌa ahiriḡano ḡoraune, ahiriḡanonoꞌo rune\f + \fr 6:8 \ft ruhuriteꞌe ḡauḡa \f* hiriviꞌuma, u Vine Zaḡoḡano ḡoraune, Vine Zaḡoḡanonoꞌo ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hiriviꞌuma.  
\v 9 Eꞌanoꞌo eme haḡai manoḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano zamafe mene zoreriꞌuma, mazaḡa eꞌe haḡaiḡa mene modine, Badiꞌaꞌa ohoniroteꞌe madaḡanoꞌe eꞌe naeḡa hiriviꞌuma.  
\v 10 Eꞌanoꞌo emeꞌa mada manoḡa ꞌahogaꞌahoga horonine, vaze niduꞌa mazao haḡai manoḡa haḡaiꞌuma. Nego nabudi fie tiburuꞌeteꞌe mazaoꞌe ufeta haḡae huniꞌuma.   
\s1 Iradugu Riḡa Ḡoeꞌa zu Uhiu Ḡoeꞌa Ḡonaga  
\p
\v 11 Ḡianoꞌi, eḡeꞌa ꞌevorehe hina zae veize ꞌahige borofe miriheꞌohe!  
\v 12 Iniuꞌe vazeꞌa niguzoga urateꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe zaeꞌa ahiri rana iḡuri haḡaoga teꞌoteꞌauꞌohe. Aꞌe, Keriso satauro harameꞌeteꞌe uꞌano hideꞌeteꞌe adugaḡa ze mene meifine raꞌohe.  
\v 13 Ahiri rana iḡuri haḡairoteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa zuni Mose goro ḡoeꞌa mene hegoteꞌe rehano, ze zaeꞌa ahiri rana iḡuri haḡaeꞌeteꞌe urateꞌohe. Aꞌe zaeꞌa zeḡe ihore hegotadu ahiri rana iḡuri haḡaeꞌeteꞌe moneo zeḡeꞌa bare niguzoga veize raꞌohe.  
\v 14 Rehano e ḡauni ꞌahoga mene hune niguneꞌohe, rehano emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Keriso satauro daꞌo niguneꞌohe. Iesu Keriso satauro uꞌano, raha gauḡa niduꞌaꞌe eḡe moneo rudaro, ebu eḡe zuni raha gauḡa niduꞌa moneo rudaro.  
\v 15 Ahiri rana iḡuri haḡaeꞌetaꞌaꞌe ga mene haḡaeꞌetaꞌaꞌe mene ḡau boro, rehano Badiꞌaꞌa haḡairoteꞌe ḡaboneḡa iziga rougaꞌe ḡau boro.  
\v 16 Badiꞌaꞌa goro ꞌahi hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa zu Badiꞌa mone azaḡa\f + \fr 6:16 \fqa Badiꞌa mone Isaraela azaḡa \f* niduꞌa zama roḡeḡa zu vetuḡa ziniꞌenoꞌi.   
\p
\v 17 Izidionoꞌo onamo zama moneo, vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa aduga ago enoꞌi, mazaḡa Iesu uꞌano meiroteꞌe bebeḡa nuꞌe ahiriheo ꞌada ꞌahine, e Iesu tuḡure vazeḡa rae ihozeꞌohe.   
\p
\v 18 Nego nabudi, emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Kerisoꞌa fureneꞌeteꞌe manoḡaḡaꞌe zae niduꞌa vineo radiuꞌenoꞌi. Amen.   